data.table 基础

data.table是data.frame的增强版。

DT = data.table(
  ID = c("b","b","b","a","a","c"),
  a = 1:6,
  b = 7:12,
  c = 13:18
)
DT

DT基本语法

DT[i, j, by]
##   R:                 i                 j        by
## SQL:  where | order by   select | update  group by

取行

不同于R中自带的数据框格式要求，如果只是取行，逗号不再是必须的。

ans <- flights[origin == "JFK" & month == 6L]
ans
ans <- flights[1:2]
ans

重新排序

ans <- flights[order(origin, -dest)]
head(ans)

取列

如果只有一列，会返回一个向量

ans <- flights[, arr_delay]
head(ans)
[1]  13  13   9 -26   1   0

若想返回data.table对象

ans <- flights[, list(arr_delay)]
head(ans)

或者使用.() 等同于list()。

ans <- flights[, .(arr_delay)]
head(ans)
ans <- flights[, .(arr_delay, dep_delay)]
head(ans)

## 等同于
# ans <- flights[, list(arr_delay, dep_delay)]

取列，同时重命名

ans <- flights[, .(delay_arr = arr_delay, delay_dep = dep_delay)]
head(ans)

列中计算 （compute or do in j）

ans <- flights[, sum( (arr_delay + dep_delay) < 0 )]
ans
[1] 141814

行列同时操作

ans <- flights[origin == "JFK" & month == 6L,
               .(m_arr = mean(arr_delay), m_dep = mean(dep_delay))]
ans
ans <- flights[origin == "JFK" & month == 6L, length(dest)]
ans
[1] 8422

特殊符号 .N

ans <- flights[origin == "JFK" & month == 6L, .N]
ans
[1] 8422

选列的不同方法

  1. 类似data.frame的方法
ans <- flights[, c("arr_delay", "dep_delay")]
head(ans)
  1. 使用..前缀
select_cols = c("arr_delay", "dep_delay")
flights[ , ..select_cols]
  1. 使用with
flights[ , select_cols, with = FALSE]
# returns year,month and day
ans <- flights[, year:day]
# returns day, month and year
ans <- flights[, day:year]
# returns all columns except year, month and day
ans <- flights[, -(year:day)]
ans <- flights[, !(year:day)]

汇总

ans <- flights[, .N, by = .(origin)]
ans
ans <- flights[carrier == "AA", .N, by = origin]
ans
ans <- flights[carrier == "AA", .N, by = .(origin, dest)]
head(ans)

行列分组汇总计算混合操作

ans <- flights[carrier == "AA",
        .(mean(arr_delay), mean(dep_delay)),
        by = .(origin, dest, month)]
ans

排序分组: keyby

data.table在分组后默认保留原先的排序情况。如果想重新分组，可以将by改为keyby：

ans <- flights[carrier == "AA",
        .(mean(arr_delay), mean(dep_delay)),
        keyby = .(origin, dest, month)]

链式操作 (chaining)

ans <- flights[carrier == "AA", .N, by = .(origin, dest)]
ans <- ans[order(origin, -dest)]
head(ans)

此处，为了排序，我们使用了中间操作，临时存储了一个ans对象后再进行排序操作。其实可以一步到位：

ans <- flights[carrier == "AA", .N, by = .(origin, dest)][order(origin, -dest)]
head(ans, 10)

分组by和表达式

列操作j可以使用表达式，分组操作by同样可以

ans <- flights[, .N, .(dep_delay>0, arr_delay>0)]
ans

j中可以用多列：.SD

比如，有100个列均值要计算。

特殊符号SD代表 Subset of Data. 其本身就是一个当前by分组结果的data.table

DT
DT[, print(.SD), by = ID]
   a b  c
1: 1 7 13
2: 2 8 14
3: 3 9 15
   a  b  c
1: 4 10 16
2: 5 11 17
   a  b  c
1: 6 12 18

因此，在多个列上做运算，可以使用lapply()

DT[, lapply(.SD, mean), by = ID]

只选择需要的列进行汇总计算 SDcols

flights[carrier == "AA",                       ## Only on trips with carrier "AA"
        lapply(.SD, mean),                     ## compute the mean
        by = .(origin, dest, month),           ## for every 'origin,dest,month'
        .SDcols = c("arr_delay", "dep_delay")] ## for just those specified in .SDcols

如何查看每个月的前两行数据

ans <- flights[, head(.SD, 2), by = month]
head(ans)

注意以下两个语法的区别：

DT[, .(val = c(a,b)), by = ID]
DT[, .(val = list(c(a,b))), by = ID]

DT的j操作非常灵活，有时候令人难以琢磨。为了更好的理解j，可以使用print函数看看究竟发生了什么

## (1) look at the difference between
DT[, print(c(a,b)), by = ID]
[1] 1 2 3 7 8 9
[1]  4  5 10 11
[1]  6 12
## (2) and
DT[, print(list(c(a,b))), by = ID]
[[1]]
[1] 1 2 3 7 8 9

[[1]]
[1]  4  5 10 11

[[1]]
[1]  6 12

记住：只要j的返回值是一个list对象，那么这个list的每个元素都将成为data.table返回值的一列。

Reference semantics

:=操作符

  1. 用法:LHS:=RHS
DT[, c("colA", "colB", ...) := list(valA, valB, ...)]

# when you have only one column to assign to you
# can drop the quotes and list(), for convenience
DT[, colA := valA]
  1. 函数形式
DT[, `:=`(colA = valA, # valA is assigned to colA
          colB = valB, # valB is assigned to colB
          ...
)]

用reference增添列变量

flights[, `:=`(speed = distance / (air_time/60), # speed in mph (mi/h)
               delay = arr_delay + dep_delay)]   # delay in minutes
head(flights)

区别在哪？ 1. 生成新变量后不需要将变量增加给flights 2. 两个新列变量已经在新的flights data.table里面了。 3. 使用函数形式的好处是可以在每个增添操作右方作注释。

sub-assign by reference

flights[hour == 24L, hour := 0L]
# := 默认不输出，可以用[]明确输出
flights[hour == 24L, hour := 0L][]

删除列 by reference

flights[, c("delay") := NULL]
head(flights)
## or using the functional form
# flights[, `:=`(delay = NULL)]

分组操作by与:=协同

flights[, max_speed := max(speed), by = .(origin, dest)]
head(flights)

多列操作与:=

对每个月计算 dep_delay and arr_delay的最大值，并新增两列变量来存储此结果。

in_cols  = c("dep_delay", "arr_delay")
out_cols = c("max_dep_delay", "max_arr_delay")
flights[, c(out_cols) := lapply(.SD, max), by = month, .SDcols = in_cols]
head(flights)

.SD 与数据分析

library(Lahman)
data(Teams)
data(Pitching)
Teams
Pitching

.SD与未分组数据

如果没有分组by信息，.SD的subsetting没有任何效果，返回的是数据本身。

identical(Pitching, Pitching[ , .SD])

.SD 与 .SDcols

Pitching[ , .SD, .SDcols = c('W', 'L', 'G')]

上面两种操作没有任何实际用处。下面开始有用的。

列类型批量转换 (batch-convert)

在数据分析中，经常需要对列（变量）的类型做强制转换，尤其是在character/factor/numeric类型间进行转换。

以下三个变量在原数据中存储类型为character，但应该转换为factor更为合理

# teamIDBR: Team ID used by Baseball Reference website
# teamIDlahman45: Team ID used in Lahman database version 4.5
# teamIDretro: Team ID used by Retrosheet
fkt = c('teamIDBR', 'teamIDlahman45', 'teamIDretro')
# confirm that they're stored as `character`
Teams[ , sapply(.SD, is.character), .SDcols = fkt]
      teamIDBR teamIDlahman45    teamIDretro 
          TRUE           TRUE           TRUE 
Teams[ , (fkt) := lapply(.SD, factor), .SDcols = fkt]
# print out the first column to demonstrate success
head(unique(Teams[[fkt[1L]]]))
[1] BOS CHI CLE KEK NYU ATH
101 Levels: ALT ANA ARI ATH ATL BAL BLA BLN BLU BOS BRA BRG BRO BSN ... WSN

(fkt)表示fkt包含的是变量名，不加括号，结果将复制给变量fkt

# while .SDcols accepts a logical vector,
#   := does not, so we need to convert to column
#   positions with which()
fkt_idx = which(sapply(Teams, is.factor))
Teams[ , (fkt_idx) := lapply(.SD, as.character), .SDcols = fkt_idx]
head(unique(Teams[[fkt_idx[1L]]]))
[1] "NA" "NL" "AA" "UA" "PL" "AL"
# [1] "NA" "NL" "AA" "UA" "PL" "AL"

可以使用正则表达式匹配列名

Teams[ , .SD, .SDcols = patterns('team')]
team_idx = grep('team', names(Teams), value = TRUE)
Teams[ , (team_idx) := lapply(.SD, factor), .SDcols = team_idx]

分组与.SD操作

Teams[ , .SD[.N], by = teamID]
Teams[ , .SD[which.max(R)], by = teamID]

key

什么是key。我们首先看一个大家都熟知的概念：行名(rownames)

set.seed(1L)
DF = data.frame(ID1 = sample(letters[1:2], 10, TRUE),
                ID2 = sample(1:3, 10, TRUE),
                val = sample(10),
                stringsAsFactors = FALSE,
                row.names = sample(LETTERS[1:10]))
DF
rownames(DF)
 [1] "I" "D" "G" "A" "B" "E" "C" "J" "F" "H"
DF["C", ]
DT = as.data.table(DF)
DT
rownames(DT)
  1. data.table从不是用行名。
  2. 如果想保留列名，可以在as.data.table()使用keep.rownames =TRUE设定。
  3. key是超级版的行名：supercharged rownames

设置key

设置key之后，data.table的行将根据reference重新排序（升序）

setkey(flights, origin)
head(flights)

设置完key之后，i操作将在key上运行。

key(flights)
[1] "origin"
flights[.("JFK")]
flights[c("JFK", "LGA")]    ## same as flights[.(c("JFK", "LGA"))]

多列key

setkey(flights, origin, dest)
head(flights)
flights[.("JFK", "MIA")]

key与j和by协同

key(flights)
[1] "origin" "dest"  
# [1] "origin" "dest"
flights[.("LGA", "TPA"), .(arr_delay)]

chaining

flights[.("LGA", "TPA"), .(arr_delay)][order(-arr_delay)]

j计算

flights[.("LGA", "TPA"), max(arr_delay)]
[1] 486

分组

setkey(flights, origin, dest)
key(flights)
ans <- flights["JFK", max(dep_delay), keyby = month]
head(ans)

其他参数：mult和nomatch

flights[.("JFK", "MIA"), mult = "first"]
flights[.(c("LGA", "JFK", "EWR"), "XNA"), mult = "last"]
flights[.(c("LGA", "JFK", "EWR"), "XNA"), mult = "last", nomatch = NULL]

secondary indices

setindex(flights, origin)
head(flights)
## alternatively we can provide character vectors to the function 'setindexv()'
# setindexv(flights, "origin") # useful to program with

# 'index' attribute added
names(attributes(flights))
[1] "names"             "row.names"         "class"            
[4] ".internal.selfref" "sorted"            "index"
